name: Basket Case (Prod. by Lil Astro)
description: Basket Case is an original animation and beat made by me for you! <3 Ownership of this NFT counts as a lease on the beat which means you can use it freely, however you don't own executive rights so others can use it as well if they also obtain a lease with their copy of this NFT. Also in order to create new content with this beat it must be in your wallet at the time of creation.
